{"tid":414401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵涌工人左手插碎肉機 消防拆開機頭解困送院","createTime":"2017-09-26T08:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T08:54:00.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5abc5d023d7896aa4576bcf8fbf8cff85615f0e0","tid":414401,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"<strong>葵涌工人左手插碎肉機 消防拆開機頭解困送院</strong><br />\n<br />\n【15：52更新】新增影片<br />\n葵涌梨木道88號達利中心一個工場，下午1時許，一名男工清潔一部碎肉機，將手插在機軸清潔之際，碎肉機突然開動，男工的左手夾在機軸內，痛極慘叫，驚動工友報警求助，消防員及救護員到場，花近句鐘拆開機頭，男工的左手仍插住機頭，一併送院，他不時臉露痛苦之情。當局正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170926/57257651\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170926%2F57257651&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsmwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=19ac9b04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170926%2F57257651&h=e1e133f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170926/57257651</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d318114659c3d2d538e9af5fd1a3140b8d4b40d3","tid":414401,"uid":12558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"皇家特工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822517e83cf3fe97b3cd37df35c1d1abc7106126","tid":414401,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T08:08:33.000Z","msg":"點會無啦啦開左架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c0ef9da38e83b7d8e7c37499593bfc11d3f78a","tid":414401,"uid":19709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T08:08:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">I WANT TO PLAY A GAME</span><img src=\"/assets/